data.description: Welcome to this exquisite ranch-style home offering a spacious and versatile layout. With 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, it's a perfect fit for families of any size. Greeted by a welcoming sitting area, the floorplan easily flows into the dining room towards the kitchen. Catering to the inner chef, this kitchen features a tile backsplash, elegant granite counters, a convenient breakfast bar, and a suite of high-end stainless steel appliances, including a double oven/convection oven/griddle/air fryer combo oven. The adjacent walk-out living room provides a cozy ambience with the brick surround gas fireplace. The majority of the home is adorned with carpeting, complemented by laminate wood flooring in the kitchen and tile in the bathrooms. The fully fenced backyard showcases an apple tree and an extended brick and concrete patio, making it an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings. Recent upgrades include new fencing, a water filtration system, a newer water heater, a water softener system, and a brand-new furnace for peace of mind. Located within walking distance of Ute Valley Park for convenient access to nature and recreation.
